Some experiments with matrix multiplication (fp32) in CUDA.
cublas only achieves a little over half of peak performance on the 3070, which
is interesting. The simple blocking outperforms this slightly.

1. simple   : straightforward blocking over global and shared-memory.
2. one-block: same as simple, but one block per streaming multiprocessor.
3. L2       : blocking over L2, simple 1D blocking
4. L2-2D    : 2D blocking over L2
